description:
Chat/Update on Twitter me: ‪http://twitter.com/beautysplurge. This is an inspired makeup look from JLo's music video, "I'm Into You." The tutorial will show how to achieve the perfect dewy glow look using a liquid illuminating product from Pixi. You can also use powder highlighter for the glow look. I prefer highlighters in liquid form because its gives a perfect finish that melts into the skin for a natural glow within.

Music: RnB Love & Torn Love
Artist: Skrip
SUBSCRIBE TO SKRIP'S CHANNEL http://www.youtube.com/skripmusic

What's on my nails? NYC One Minute Polish in Sidewalker

Circle lens? Hana SPC Hyper Natural Brown Lens
Visit ‪http://www.candylens.com/products/Han...‬‬ for 5% off on your purchase by entering Promotional Code: beautysplurge

Makeup:
-Laura Mercier Tinted Moisturizer in Sand (Sephora)
-Pixi Illuminating Tinted Moisturizer in Nude GLow (Target or http://www.pixibeauty.com)
-Pixi Nude Wardrobe Palette (Target or http://www.pixibeauty.com)
-Urban Decay eyeliner in Zero & Whiskey (Ulta)
-NYX eyeliner in Baby Pink (Ulta)
-Salon Perfect Prefectly Glamourous False Lashes (Walmart)
-Sonia Kashuk taupe brow pencil (Target)
-ELF Brow Gel (Target or http://www.eyeslipsface.com)
-Revlon Luscious Mascara in blackest black (Target)
-NARS Laguna Bronzer (Sephora)
-NARS Orgasm Multiple Blush (Sephora)
-MAC Creme D Nude lipstick (Nordstrom)
-Benefits Juicy Coral lipgloss (Sephora)

Recorded with Canon Vixia HF S-21 camcorder and edited with Final Cut Studio.

Disclaimer: This is an inspired look from a beach scene in "I'm Into You" music video and not intended to look just like Jennifer Lopez.

FTC: I purchased all of the items presented in this video. I was not compensated by any of these companies that are seen in this video.
